  <h3>Project Structure</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>src/assets/icons</strong> - SVG icons for your project</li>
    <li><strong>src/assets/images</strong> - Images for your project</li>
    <li><strong>src/styles</strong> - SCSS stylesheets</li>
    <li><strong>src/data</strong> - JSON data</li>
    <li><strong>src/templates/layouts</strong> - Twig layouts</li>
    <li><strong>src/templates/partials</strong> - Twig partials</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Available Commands</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><code>npm start</code> - Start development server</li>
    <li><code>npm run build</code> - Build for production</li>
    <li><code>npm run preview</code> - Preview production build</li>
    <li><code>npm run lint</code> - Lint HTML</li>
    <li><code>npm run lint:fix</code> - Fix HTML linting issues</li>
    <li><code>npm run stylelint</code> - Lint CSS</li>
    <li><code>npm run stylelint:fix</code> - Fix CSS linting issues</li>
  </ul>

